data.description: OPEN HOUSE (SAT 11/11 - 12:45-2:45pm) PRICE DROP 8k!! Now 210k  Check out this turn key 3 bed 1 bath Port Richmond home. This straight through design offers a big living room and dining room area.   Hard wood floors through out. All the bed rooms are good sized. The bathroom was recently redone. The basement is Immaculate. Perfect for a man cave or plenty of storage space.  There is a cemented r.ear yard. The porch front over looks the playground. Convenient for the kids, exercising etc. Parking is easier with the playground out front. Minutes from I-95, Betsy Ross Bridge(to NJ)  and the Aramingo Shopping district makes the location perfect. You can be in center city Phila in or NE Phila(via I-95/Aramingo Ave) in 10-15 mins depending on the time of the day. Plenty of bus transportation(SEPTA) on Aramingo Ave or Richmond Street. We offer grant $ for 1st time home buyers so miss the opportunity to own this maintenance free home. Why not own this home verses renting a home.  Development is in the area so this is a good long term investment.
